short_summary: The Government of Canada requires an acquisition and service contract for an Enterprise Architecture Software Solution (EASS) that is fully compatible with QualiWare product and corresponding metamodel content.
description: The Government of Canada seeks to acquire software to aid in understanding their organizational and technical architecture. The requirement includes ongoing maintenance and support. Furthermore, they seek access to training to ensure required skills are developed and maintained for professional services related to this contract. The contract delivers and mixes these requirements under one package. The scope of the contract includes ongoing professional support services and maintenance. The objective is to aid the Government of Canada in digital transformation missions, providing integrated platform and accompanying services for the end user to configure, customize, and organize their tools, expanding their operational network within the specified limits.
